long_description: Take the Ahnu Del Rey Sandals through the woods or up the river. They're designed to keep your feet centered for a natural stride with great underfoot support and comfort. Mesh uppers dry quickly so you can travel comfortably in and out of the water. Webbing strap system on the tops and adjustable heel straps ensure a snug, comfortable fit. EVA midsoles provide cushion; nylon shanks protect your feet from stone bruising. Ahnu Del Rey Sandals have rubber toe caps that protect your toes from impacts.
